Installation of Prometheus on Ubuntu 24.04
By default prometheus is available at apt repository. 

Update the apt repository ( sudo apt update -y && apt upgrade -y).

Install the prometheus using apt package manager ( sudo apt install prometheus prometheus-node-exporter -y)

Enable the prometheus (sudo systemcl enable --now prometheus prometheus-node-exporter)

Check the status of prometheus. (sudo systemctl status prometheus prometheus-node-exporter)

Access the prometheus form outside. (http://publicIP:9090).
